// Copy this file to DevelopmentTeam.xcconfig and replace the value with your
// own Apple Developer Team ID. You can find it in Xcode under Settings →
// Accounts → (your Apple ID) → Manage Certificates, or in the Apple Developer
// portal at developer.apple.com/account.
//
// Free "Personal Team" accounts work fine for personal/local use; the cert
// rotates every 7 days, so the bridge needs a rebuild weekly.
DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = YOUR_TEAM_ID_HERE
